{"tid":2226591,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"原神：才兩天我就患上這些毛病，實在是不敢玩下去！","createTime":"2020-10-02T06:11:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T06:19:13.000Z","uid":25345,"like":1,"dislike":142,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"aad9abc1092937f32a5c5e3c79ae6ef298ea1443","tid":2226591,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T06:11:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/12548758873/1000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Finews.gtimg.com%2Fnewsapp_bt%2F0%2F12548758873%2F1000&h=2d4eccce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小編玩到現在才18級，真的是小白玩家啥都不懂，到現在才知道這個游戲真的很讓人入迷，尤其是這五個毛病玩過的絕對都有！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一、不斷抽卡<br />\n<br />\n一入抽卡深似海啊，尤其是原神這種低概率的，沒拿到笛姥爺真的很不甘心，為什麼別人人品都那麼好，而我們就只能拿個四星，實在是不爽啊！還是接著抽吧，接著氪金吧！<br />\n<img src=\"http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/12548758871/1000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Finews.gtimg.com%2Fnewsapp_bt%2F0%2F12548758871%2F1000&h=03b8e448&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n二、不斷解密<br />\n<br />\n原神有很多的任務，尤其觸發似的想多得多，但是完成的難度是相當的高，相當的費時間，如果是你一個人探索花一個小時還可能完成不了，尤其是這個古雲有璃，最後那三個碎片的位置相當費腦，還有方位點亮....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/12548758872/1000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Finews.gtimg.com%2Fnewsapp_bt%2F0%2F12548758872%2F1000&h=3a35d88d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n三、不斷看風景<br />\n<br />\n原神的世界觀相當的大，這也造就地圖實在是走不完啊，風景相當的漂亮，很多都是可以拿來當壁紙的，美不勝收！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/12548758869/1000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Finews.gtimg.com%2Fnewsapp_bt%2F0%2F12548758869%2F1000&h=57a22d6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n四、不斷尋找寶箱<br />\n<br />\n這個絕對是強迫症，看到寶箱就邁不動腿的大有人在，不過這個游戲是真的摳門，華麗寶箱就給我們幾個垃圾東西，實在是令人失望。不過下回看到寶箱還是想去拿啊，這個該怎麼治呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/12548758886/1000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Finews.gtimg.com%2Fnewsapp_bt%2F0%2F12548758886%2F1000&h=96d2d20c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n五、不斷尋找風神或者岩神瞳<br />\n<br />\n太難了太多了，本來以為就幾個，沒想到最後一查這種東西都上百個了，有些還要靠技巧去拿，前期不知道做標記，後期看攻略還得一個一個再重新去找，真的很累。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/12548758877/1000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Finews.gtimg.com%2Fnewsapp_bt%2F0%2F12548758877%2F1000&h=70a29dc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以勸告各位萌新想入坑的，要三思而後行，這個游戲有毒容易上癮，尤其是這五個要慎重要量力！"},{"pid":"d3cac61c9e0252dcc379148cbff2f1b7e77c1b95","tid":2226591,"uid":31215,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T06:13:25.000Z","msg":"連登仔第一個唔玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c11bac4cfcabab7b05af3e2a956aadefe7515b5","tid":2226591,"uid":3513,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T06:19:18.000Z","msg":"又毒又柒又要課金抽卡 <br />\n後門俾人裝埋毒 你玩埋我個份"},{"pid":"2b0ab3846ddec018a63f1b3b5f8a488f12411fcf","tid":2226591,"uid":76848,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T06:48:37.000Z","msg":"無好靚咋喎 <br />\n壁紙呢句個個都copy <br />\n咁撚環保<br />\n唔好出錢俾班writers 啦"},{"pid":"47d2231fec53c8a791887541dcf3dd8eb89ba24f","tid":2226591,"uid":85180,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T06:51:29.000Z","msg":"【又爆醜聞】內地遊戲《原神》被揭竊玩家私隱 反作弊機制出事<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2226085\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2226085</a>"},{"pid":"2b7bc737b76ca97abce0f4e430c319837014189a","tid":2226591,"uid":52939,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T07:25:37.000Z","msg":"狗也不屌"},{"pid":"c9b0ca22ee8942d4ea71933d04ff3d3d8f13d9bc","tid":2226591,"uid":283385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T07:29:53.000Z","msg":"樓主無玩過gta?  <br />\n大陸野狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5f2dfe537945f5d56402b7cfbe5b7e4dc8a3ebf","tid":2226591,"uid":278184,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T07:38:25.000Z","msg":"曲直難分<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d213bb3049ba4a54e1b38a1a471864fa021ca5d","tid":2226591,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T08:07:41.000Z","msg":"廣告編<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cad61ed1ad7a633f451d9bb1dbca68b4242049d9","tid":2226591,"uid":155374,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T14:34:11.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">成日換個標題又再宣傳，收皮啦，屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"674c6e57515befd500d0656ccfd1b101b9b4dcb9","tid":2226591,"uid":346701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T06:19:13.000Z","msg":"第六<br />\n可以被裝後門<br />\n你開心我開心習近平也開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}